//fields such as minRate, maxRate, minFee, maxFee, and isRequired to validate the

request.description: The options available in the Pricing API may differ based on the integrator and can be retrieved from the PricingPlanTemplate/All endpoint as a PricingPlanTemplate. We recommend dynamically constructing a PricingPlan for your merchant based on the options returned to you from this endpoint. As an example, this request retrieves the a PricingPlanTemplate, the accompanying test maps the values from the PricingPlanTemplate into a PricingPlan, and then the following request sends that PricingPlan back.

item.name: Pricing - Create Pricing Plan Using Template
